{"tid":1490972,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"明顯兩個酷刑垃圾唔係第一次咁做","createTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T21:20:06.000Z","uid":55019,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fea7be6e1c63810ad19cdb0392767d42ca10d3ed","tid":1490972,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"手法既純粹殘忍毫不留手可見一班 <br />\n<br />\n知法犯法係咪要坐返十年八年？"},{"pid":"b861ce4ba0c9aa75e98244456532eee36aaed32d","tid":1490972,"uid":203417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:04:34.000Z","msg":"坐一世啦屌"},{"pid":"35f9565f0bbd7c165b0c8e5680fd8ef6e80ed143","tid":1490972,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"手法純熟到"},{"pid":"7395589e6c8d3ba03c5dd176194f6a782729da1a","tid":1490972,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:29:11.000Z","msg":"其中一條撚樣仲要係好後生 垃圾黑警一返工就教D新仔做呢D野"},{"pid":"79cb8248ecde08af8f4945be5a8b08b3e89840a9","tid":1490972,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"成立獨立委員會既訴求要改成：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將狗隊隊長連同有關狗隻送到海牙軍事法庭受審</span></span><br />\n<br />\n任何形式之本地法律制度已經失效<br />\n<br />\n任何平台,委員會都只係閉門做車,香港人不要接受。<br />\n<br />\n有意圖打爆記者既眼同行刺記者至危殆,已經要按戰犯看待。"},{"pid":"a3b6109a355d65d93dd340cad1dd94af72b2a635","tid":1490972,"uid":193328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:30:30.000Z","msg":"分分鐘上司收左利益唔告發下屬，到有CCTV先無法，ICAC見啦"},{"pid":"86a1c98a86113970fc283e5c2b51fedabaab12da","tid":1490972,"uid":50904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"當年暗角七警係告呢條「有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害罪」<br />\n最高可判處終身監禁，之但係被告係黑警的話..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017/02/17   杜官又指，曾健超當時被扣上膠手銬，並無防範能力，而眾被告當時是惡意襲擊曾健超，萬幸是曾健超沒有受更大傷害。法官以2年6個月作量判起點，考慮被告長時間服務社會、初犯、佔中時承受壓力，而警員勢將被警隊解僱，及失去退休金等，故減刑6個月至2年<br />\n2019/07/26 上訴庭指七警案原審法官以兩年判刑作量刑起點是過高<br />\n<br />\n綁住你黎圍毆都係判2年，之後再有得減刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[回帶警世] 暗角七警案 落案拖1年 2年後正式開審 5年後上訴得直獲減刑</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1491009\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1491009</a><br />\n<br />\n我專登去搵返2014年暗角七警案嘅新聞標題，希望幫大家清醒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算拉左人，警隊、律政師、政府、中共係一定會全力包庇佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗開工都有糧出唔在講，仲一定會用最貴嘅律師去打官司，未判刑就籌好安家費，然後拖返幾年等件事淡左就順便上訴減刑，再復職開工受到英雄式待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3708821e7db1cf22f8ab7545078734840d940c9","tid":1490972,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fea7be6e1c63810ad19cdb0392767d42ca10d3ed","tid":1490972,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"手法既純粹殘忍毫不留手可見一班 <br />\n<br />\n知法犯法係咪要坐返十年八年？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"係終身"},{"pid":"2ebddc6a44da8ad68dfa319eda9050152d129686","tid":1490972,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3708821e7db1cf22f8ab7545078734840d940c9","tid":1490972,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fea7be6e1c63810ad19cdb0392767d42ca10d3ed","tid":1490972,"uid":55019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"手法既純粹殘忍毫不留手可見一班 <br />\n<br />\n知法犯法係咪要坐返十年八年？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"係終身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"酷刑罪 判終身"},{"pid":"79515c7821f1fc05609e5e2de815f39c2b4e33c8","tid":1490972,"uid":307857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"宜家踢緊冰島對鍠馬<br />\n<br />\n只係踢到中場休息,重有下半場<br />\n<br />\n球証全部都係對面d人<br />\n<br />\n成隊有700人受傷<br />\n<br />\n互無入球<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">輸左呢場波,就會俾金仔捉去打靶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n隨時比死更難受<br />\n<br />\n冰島=兼職義士<br />\n鍠馬=職業殺手<br />\n<br />\n金仔=共產主義"},{"pid":"124fb513815304fc529787b4dafc2e0fac9f5bcb","tid":1490972,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"去遊行成日聽到人大叫 香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n聽到都尷尬 錯曬重點<br />\n佢地係執法犯法 ok？ 知法犯法係低一個層次"},{"pid":"dee3ee84c004f28f435540edf9101a40d5636976","tid":1490972,"uid":30837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"有警犬fd話比人拉果兩件係岩岩做無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcf08b6e1d37e07abc619c4435bf3e94ca189fb","tid":1490972,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"好明顯呢啲行為喺警隊好普遍，尤如文化<br />\n<br />\n有系統地侵犯人權，施加酷刑"},{"pid":"df7b4737ec94949008a2cf9d6a34299514060871","tid":1490972,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"依間病房有冇多d以前既片睇到，可能有意外發現"},{"pid":"eb5c4f24673ce9c2a366a8cea948963a439d6aee","tid":1490972,"uid":100273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"佢地應該係慣犯，唔係第一次，否則唔會係同袍面前做<br />\n如果係第一次，會因為唔肯定包袍立場而有所顧忌<br />\n所以有理由相信佢地一向都係咁ge方式對犯，好似拍戲咁"},{"pid":"54c7f5ea5dafc6f18206b85bc1ac2362977667fe","tid":1490972,"uid":258421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fcf08b6e1d37e07abc619c4435bf3e94ca189fb","tid":1490972,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"好明顯呢啲行為喺警隊好普遍，尤如文化<br />\n<br />\n有系統地侵犯人權，施加酷刑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:43:09.000Z","msg":"我同事十幾廿年前入過臭格，佢話好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb6f5727a2f9694be9995fe24461ba3151c4f25","tid":1490972,"uid":293261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo